description: Let F(x) = 1+1*x+4*x^2+10*x^3+ ..., the g.f. for A000293 (solid partitions), and write F(x) = 1/prod(n>=1, (1-x^n)^a(n) ).

D. E. Knuth, A Note on Solid Partitions, Math. Comp. 24, 955-961, 1970.
